_______________________________________________________________________________
"Mental Blow"     
        This sends a hammering blow of force directly into the mind of
        the target.  It does a base amount of damage slightly dependent
        upon regular level and does a further random amount based on
        guild level.  It is an all around attack power cheaper and faster
        than psionic blast.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  3		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  mblow <target>
